| !Help for PipeDream
|
| Determine style of help (text or HTML)
If "<File$Type_FAF>"="" Then Set PipeDream$HelpSuffix Text Else Set PipeDream$HelpSuffix HTML.index/html
|
| Try locating help on resources path
Set PipeDream$HelpFile PipeDreamRes:Help.<PipeDream$HelpSuffix>
|
| Fallback is direct (path may not be set)
IfThere <PipeDream$HelpFile> Then Else Set PipeDream$HelpFile <Obey$Dir>.Res.UK.Help.<PipeDream$HelpSuffix>
|
Unset PipeDream$HelpSuffix
|
IfThere <PipeDream$HelpFile> Then Filer_Run <PipeDream$HelpFile> Else Error Help not found
